            "question": "How Long Do Weed Gummies Take to Kick In?",
            "answer": "<p>Weed gummies typically take 30 to 90 minutes to kick in, depending on factors like metabolism, body weight, and whether you've eaten recently. Unlike smoking, edibles need to be digested, so patience is key.</p>"
