        "faq_block_3i3brd": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "What Are The Benefits of Edible Weed Gummies?",
            "answer": "<p>Edible THC gummies offer several benefits, including pain relief, reduced anxiety and stress, improved sleep, and appetite stimulation. They are also effective in alleviating nausea and vomiting, particularly for chemotherapy patients. Gummies provide a convenient and discreet consumption method, with long-lasting effects that can help manage chronic conditions without the need for smoking or vaping.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_block_q3NgVT": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "How Strong Are Kush Queen’s Weed Gummies?",
            "answer": "<p>Kush Queen Weed Gummies come in a variety of formulations, primarily featuring Delta 9 THC combined with CBD. Each gummy contains 8mg of Delta 9 THC and 12mg of CBD, designed to offer strong psychoactive effects along with significant relaxation. The combination aims to provide both euphoria and the therapeutic benefits of CBD​.</p><p>The Delta 9 THC content in these gummies is compliant with federal regulations, containing less than 0.3% THC by dry weight, making them legally available for purchase online in most areas​​. For new users, it's recommended to start with half a gummy to assess tolerance, as the effects can last around four hours and include a notable shift in mood and relaxation​​.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_block_yiA8Rm": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "How Many Weed Gummies Should I Take for My First Time?",
            "answer": "<p>For first-time users, start with a low dose, usually 2.5 to 5 mg of THC. Wait at least two hours before considering another dose. Remember, you can always take more, but you can’t undo taking too much. The Kush Queen rule of thumb for new users is always, \"Start low and go slow.\"</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_block_gqBR9U": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "How Long Do the Effects of Weed Gummies Last?",
            "answer": "<p>The effects of weed gummies can last anywhere from 4 to 8 hours, with the peak effects usually occurring 2 to 4 hours after consumption. Duration varies based on dosage, metabolism, and tolerance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_block_3tebeq": {
          "type": "faq_block",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "Are Weed Gummies Safe to Consume?",
            "answer": "<p>Weed gummies are safe when consumed responsibly. It's crucial to follow dosing guidelines, avoid mixing with alcohol or other substances, and store them out of reach of children and pets.</p>"
